        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Samuel Mifflin (born Samuel Mifflin Francis) was the son of Colonel Turbutt Francis and Sarah Mifflin, and the grandson of Tench Francis and Elizabeth Turbutt, and of Colonel Samuel Mifflin.</p>
